research_municipality_step.notes: The Mayor, Patricia Finstrom, was confirmed as Mayor-elect in May 2024. The list of Aldermen is primarily based on the Texas State Directory Online. Ward designations for some Aldermen were found in the TML City Officials Directory. While one source mentions 'single-member wards', other sources list multiple aldermen for the same ward. The provided designations reflect the information found for each individual.
